{"name": "odoo-addon-mrp-subcontracting-purchase-link", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-mrp-subcontracting-purchase-link", "version": "16.0.1.0.0.10", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPLv3)", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/manufacture", "license": "LGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Link Purchase Order Line to Subcontract Productions", "upload_time": 1719719572}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-LGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: LGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fmanufacture-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/manufacture\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/manufacture/tree/16.0/mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/manufacture-16-0/manufacture-16-0-mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/manufacture&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Link Purchase Order Line to Subcontract Productions\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:fcb1900c633f34a9bad831462e059fb9d5e537bd609cc618abc48e86a49175be\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module does the following:\n\n- Extends \\_prepare_subcontract_mo_vals() and adds the purchase order line reference to the subcontracted manufacturing orders.\n- Adds an action button in the purchase order form view to open related subcontracted manufacturing orders.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/manufacture/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/manufacture/issues/new?body=module:%20mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Quartile Limited\n- ForgeFlow\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Quartile Limited](https://www.quartile.co):\n\n  - Yoshi Tashiro \\<<mailto:tashiro@quartile.co>>\n  - Tim Lai \\<<mailto:tl@quartile.com>>\n\n- [ForgeFlow](https://www.forgeflow.com):\n\n  - Thiago Mulero \\<<mailto:thuago.mulero@forgeflow.com>>\n  - Jordi Ballester \\<<mailto:jordi.ballester@forgeflow.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/manufacture](https://github.com/OCA/manufacture/tree/16.0/mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.mrp_production", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models..mrp_production", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.purchase_order", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models..purchase_order", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.stock_picking", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models..stock_picking", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.stock_picking", "documentation": ["Copyright 2020 Quartile Limited", "License LGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.stock_picking.StockPicking", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.stock_picking.StockPicking._prepare_subcontract_mo_vals", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "subcontract_move", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "bom", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.stock_picking.StockPicking._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_subcontracting_purchase_link.models.purchase_order", "documentation": ["Copyright 2020 Quartile Limited", "License LGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl)